snippet.title: "AMBER'S CRAZY!" Amber Heard's EX EXPOSES HER LIES about Johnny Depp! | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
"AMBER'S CRAZY!" Amber Heard's EX EXPOSES HER LIES about Johnny Depp! | Celebrity Craze

Amber Heard is exposed again. The Amber Heard Johnny Depp Drama continues. This time it is Amber Heard's ex lover who is coming out to expose her. He had some interesting things to say about Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's relationship. She might be caught in her lies again. Is Amber Heard fired or trying to cancel herself with all these lies? Let's break it down in today's video.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.
